## Decision

v0.1 cannot close. The current full suite and isolated wheel-completeness test
pass, but the frame requires `pytest_random_order_passes_3_seeds` and the local
test environment exposes no random-order pytest option/plugin. Because that
predicate cannot be evaluated, the frame is blocked until the random-order gate
is installed or the frame is amended.

